description: Architecture guidelines for Elixir + Phoenix projects
globs:
  - lib/**
  - test/**
  - config/**
  - mix.exs
  - mix.lock
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use Phoenix Contexts to separate domain logic:
  - `lib/my_app/` — core domain.
  - `lib/my_app_web/` — web layer (controllers, views, live views, templates).
- Ecto schemas live in `lib/my_app/` under appropriate context modules.
- Tests live in `test/` and follow ExUnit conventions.
- Prefer small, focused modules.
- Follow community conventions (https://hexdocs.pm/phoenix/contexts.html).
